Use the following to "install" this package into your bashrc:

INSTALL_DIR=$HOME/.programming-wisdom
git clone https://github.com/jhaberstroh/programming-wisdom $INSTALL_DIR
echo "shuf -n 1 $INSTALL_DIR/wisdom.txt | cowsay" >> ~/.bashrc

You can change INSTALL_DIR to any absolute directory you would like to install into.

Happy coding!!
